"3 pounds chicken pieces, skinned","2 cups thinly sliced onion","3/4 teaspoon salt","1/2 teaspoon coarsely ground black pepper","3 (14.5-ounce) cans  fat-free, lower-sodium chicken broth","4  garlic cloves, crushed","3  bell peppers, seeded and chopped","1  bay leaf","1 (15-ounce) can golden or white hominy, drained","2 tablespoons ground guajillo chile powder","1 1/2 teaspoons dried oregano","1/2 cup roasted unsalted pumpkinseed kernels","1/4 cup chopped fresh cilantro","1/4 cup sliced radishes","1/4 cup sliced scallions","1/2 cup crumbled queso fresco cheese"